'''Uruguay''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in June 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Montevideo, along with Punta del Este and Salto.

On June 9, 2019 on [[IOS version|iOS]]; new countries were added. Along with Uruguay; there was also [[Afghanistan]], [[Belgium]], [[Djibouti]], [[Dominican Republic]], [[Iraq]], [[Poland]], [[Puerto Rico]], [[Switzerland]], [[Taiwan]], [[Thailand]], and [[United Arab Emirates]]. It was added to Android September 21, 2019. In the [[Challenges|420 challenge]], Uruguay is one of many nations where cannabis is legal.
